<body><div class="container"><h1 id="an-act-respecting-the-fundamental-aspects-of-model-canada">An Act respecting the fundamental aspects of Model Canada</h1>



<h2 id="a-bill-prepared-by-the-special-committee-on-constitutional-affairs"><em>A bill prepared by the Special Committee on Constitutional Affairs</em></h2>

